test_zero_range:
assert [0, 0] == []
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 0
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [0, 0]
test_even_range:
assert [12, 14] == [12, 14, 16]
  Right contains one more item: 16
  Full diff:
  - [12, 14, 16]
  ?        ----
  + [12, 14]
test_large_range:
assert [6, 7] == [6, 7, 8]
  Right contains one more item: 8
  Full diff:
  - [6, 7, 8]
  ?      ---
  + [6, 7]
